WEBVTT


00:00:00.200 --> 00:00:02.920
Homeschooling is the next route,

00:00:02.920 --> 00:00:04.920
which is exploding in the United States.

00:00:04.920 --> 00:00:07.240
I mean, it's just growing so rapidly,

00:00:07.240 --> 00:00:09.960
and technology has put us in a position to

00:00:09.960 --> 00:00:11.320
where we can do that.

00:00:11.320 --> 00:00:13.240
We have options that were created,

00:00:13.240 --> 00:00:16.080
infrastructure to deliver education to kids at home

00:00:16.080 --> 00:00:17.600
that didn't exist before.

00:00:17.600 --> 00:00:19.300
And I think those trends will continue.
